            {
              "message": "`plan.md`/`impl-plan.json` present T001 as only in progress, but the generated `usecase-types.md` now marks every T001 usecase catalogue entry as Blue instead of Yellow. In this workflow Yellow is the WIP declaration state and Blue is the implemented/confirmed state, so the plan artifacts now give conflicting status signals for the same T001 work and can falsely present the usecase contract as already complete.",
              "severity": "P1",
